Ivo sambi yokuwa yowoneka kuwa wanhu wamwenga wezakwingila muna ikaye iyo, na waja wa mwanduso wowahulike Mbuli Inogile hawadahile kwingila kwaviya hawamtegeleze.
Mulungu kagesa siku imwenga, "Diyelo" Kalonga kufosela Daudi miyaka mingi hamwande, fana viilongigwe mwanduso, "Diyelo one muhahulika dizi jake, sekemwingile mizoyo yenu midala."
Kwaviya one Yoshua yaweng'hile wanhu wa Isilaeliaruhulo, Mulungu sigambe yalonge mbuli ya siku dimwenga hamwande.
