na Bulahimu kamwing'ha Zakaliya fungu da longo da vinhu vose vovilawilile. Wa mwanduso, zina jake Melikisadeki fambulo jake "Mfalume wa Yolonda Mulungu," na kaidi "Mfalume wa Salemi" fambulo jake "Mfalume wa Tindiwalo."
